{"type": "article", "id": 4734, "title": "Wall Ride 滑板收纳架", "description": "", "date": "2014-12-26T08:00:34Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 11, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233540iu8pbRFIs3rO1yJX.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;line-height:normal;\">\r\n\t见到过许多极具设计感的滑板，却从未听说过有滑板收纳工具这种东西。日前，来自意大利都灵的设计工作室 Zanocchi &amp; Starke 就推出了一款名为「Wall Ride」的滑板收纳工具，可以将其挂在墙面上，除了收纳滑板之外，设计师还贴心地为其设计了收纳架与挂钩，可以将一些小物件收纳其中。如果你的滑板足够美貌，搭配着这样一款简约的收纳装置挂在家中，也是个不错的装饰呢。如需购买，请联系 studio@zanocchistarke.com。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;line-height:normal;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233537uadsfFcjb04UQEHS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7328125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052335383I8pkGb7NQeS1KLm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7328125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233539CLJFd6UOaMSsK9qW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7328125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052335390KZxJHBvOXLEDMhN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7328125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}